我生来就是王者。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','镰鼬',NULL,NULL),(44,'chenmotong','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','陈墨瞳','/uploads/avatars/1b8e33c2164c423ab3c6c482a7db728e.jpg','A','学生会',1,0,'USER','红色高跟鞋不是张扬，只是今天心情好罢了。而我的心情，你永远猜不透。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','侧写',NULL,NULL),(45,'fingel_von','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','芬格尔','/uploads/avatars/4ace84889c184111b14baec215dfc854.jpg','A','执行部',1,0,'USER','卡塞尔学院最久的留级生，F级战神，情报之王。别问我为什么还没毕业——问就是在执行秘密任务。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:47:35','青铜御座',NULL,'2026-07-11 07:44:15'),(46,'xiami_yemeng','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','夏弥','/uploads/avatars/8fd7a06c7bdd4da19c3563b8b6a02a4d.jpg','S','狮心会',1,0,'USER','风王之瞳，永伴君焰','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','风王之瞳',NULL,NULL),(47,'rainata','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','零','https://patchwiki.biligame.com/images/lzkp/5/5e/9qgypa3n20fbozv2go24ywsxjlj2nci.png','A','学生会',1,0,'USER','我不需要朋友，也不需要回忆。但如果你请我吃冰淇淋，我可以考虑多看你一眼。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','镜瞳',NULL,NULL),(49,'prof_schneider','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','施耐德教授','https://patchwiki.biligame.com/images/lzkp/0/06/5nxyjnkrzzuvul6g8dmxuifm9lnnpxo.png','B','教授',1,0,'USER','执行部没有温柔可言。每一次任务都可能是最后一次。戴着呼吸机说话是我的特权。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','无',NULL,NULL),(50,'prof_manstein','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','曼施坦因教授','https://patchwiki.biligame.com/images/lzkp/0/06/5nxyjnkrzzuvul6g8dmxuifm9lnnpxo.png','B','教授',1,0,'USER','纪律是卡塞尔的基石。风纪委员会的眼睛无处不在——包括你正在看的这条签名。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','无',NULL,NULL),(51,'eriyi','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','上杉绘梨衣','/uploads/avatars/ca66b59d83de4820a6de0337f5f126bb.jpg','S','执行部',1,0,'USER','世界很温柔，因为有小怪兽。绘梨衣最喜欢尼桑了，尼桑说要好好活下去。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','审判',NULL,NULL),(52,'luomingze','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','路鸣泽','https://patchwiki.biligame.com/images/lzkp/1/1e/5og9emplh2w5m5thcw8ls37u67sqge7.png','S','学生会',1,0,'USER','哥哥，你又遇到麻烦了吧？四分之一的生命，换一个奇迹，很划算的买卖哦。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','全部',NULL,NULL),(53,'parsifal','$2b$10$4iHTdd2bkG5b8DqigmgA8OJhO2mwiDAvlc2okN/0gE48PwheBMZdm','帕西','https://patchwiki.biligame.com/images/lzkp/5/5e/2c3iwc0uhloiblzelh52u1ojsqdf0u9.png','A','执行部',1,0,'USER','加图索家的影子，从不站在阳光下。但影子，往往比主人更了解这个世界的规则。','2026-07-11 07:20:46','2026-07-11 07:28:27','无',NULL,NULL),(74,'XiaMu','$2a$10$7ZCgttABR1nIAdcwkIPV1uZP2wo255ki8AsjLNJWUU5LLqOplGkwy','夏目','/uploads/avatars/14109cb5cc9746f7ae60f72c5665d3b2.jpg','D','',1,0,'USER',NULL,'2026-07-11 09:03:48','2026-07-11 09:03:48','言灵·影',NULL,NULL),(75,'CunYu','$2a$10$AKd1pGDaU7eI.l5Ysd6bZ.3eUwbhM58.sEBZKgwxGHSJiAPTe5ou.','村雨','/uploads/avatars/0ce18687e3c5464b9d1ffcb2ccfdb2ee.jpg','B','学生会',1,1,'USER','寸雨握在手中的时候，我就已经没有退路了。','2026-07-11 09:54:13','2026-07-12 10:53:12','雷池',NULL,'2026-07-12 10:53:13'),(76,'8006147','$2a$10$pNsMq8QNikbdPZB15.o7puO9H9PoSYLRvLSY0aMArz7q/cab0Alwu','拉面委员会主席','/uploads/avatars/98ea6a9331d84580a75e57b929a71be0.jpg','S','教授',1,0,'USER',NULL,'2026-07-11 11:08:01','2026-07-11 15:23:26','言灵·审判',NULL,'2026-07-11 15:20:11'),(77,'Vellyn Kryos','$2a$10$Ra/qsOIeMuWepIeg5cGTI.N2k4tTJYGS9ynwbHjry003YmTdVNeDy','白咲','/uploads/avatars/8d2d32aabc4e4ebdae5187770754794f.jpg','S','执行部',1,0,'USER','还没到来的未来，转眼就是现在\n','2026-07-11 12:03:19','2026-07-12 10:40:37','言灵·皇帝',NULL,'2026-07-12 10:37:29'),(78,'斩龙者','$2a$10$CXCH78zhFv0GLbA88Qj83uwTTfb10K.wVmmf8rcaW9bya2uWwsXka','最后的黄昏','','A','狮心会',1,0,'USER','干枯的玫瑰，唤醒自卑的王','2026-07-11 13:09:15','2026-07-11 13:33:15','言灵·因陀罗',NULL,'2026-07-11 13:29:41'),(79,'汤元馅紫薯','$2a$10$YFYwtuDeWqNGZMIxcA0CCOb2qE5E2fvXE0KKmvZUrAL5C7/p50Tsy','汤元馅紫薯',NULL,'A',NULL,1,0,'USER',NULL,'2026-07-11 13:19:55','2026-07-11 20:34:11','言灵·因陀罗',NULL,'2026-07-11 20:31:11'),(80,'因陀罗','$2a$10$17O9NZ0PjDOC1yzoZDP0iORG8zwn